   Ok, there will be conditional increments and decrements, I've found a 
way to do it without too much inelegance.  Means there will be things like:

	<decc N1> decrement counter N1 if response correct
	<decw N1> decrement counter N1 if response wrong
	<decnr N1> decrement counter N1 if response no response
	<incc N1> increment counter N1 if response correct
	<incw N1> increment counter N1 if response wrong
	<incnr N1> increment counter N1 if response no response

-jonathan (j.c.f.)

